<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,191,366,388]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">3(2)</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,843,396,418]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">(a) Fore, mid and usually hind femora largely marked with black.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,1326,425,447]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(b) Head with clypeus widely yellow medially and frons almost entirely black (
<figureCitation box="[975,1035,425,447]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 3b). … 
<taxonomicName box="[1118,1267,425,447]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphiliidae" genus="Onycholyda" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viriditibialis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1118,1267,425,447]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">O. viriditibialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, p. 66
</paragraph>
</keyLead>
<keyLead pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[151,707,455,477]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">— (aa) Femora entirely pale yellow or greenish yellow.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,751,484,506]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(bb) Head color pattern different (
<figureCitation box="[527,587,484,506]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 4a, b–5aa). … 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[739,751,484,505]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">4</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</keyLead>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<keyLead pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
