</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,769,543,565]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(a) Anterior margin of clypeus pale yellow (
<figureCitation box="[638,698,543,565]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 4a, b).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,908,572,594]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(b) Median ocellus surrounded by large pale yellow mark (
<figureCitation box="[778,838,572,594]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 4a, b).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,1306,601,623]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(c) Clypeus rather smooth, with inconspicuous surface microsculpture and sparse punctures. ... 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Shinohara" authorityYear="1988" box="[1130,1246,601,622]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphiliidae" genus="Pamphilius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zinovjevi">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1130,1246,601,622]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">O. zinovjevi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, p. 67
</paragraph>
</keyLead>
<keyLead pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[151,1271,631,653]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
– (aa) Anterior margin of clypeus with obscure pale yellow spot at middle or entirely black (
<figureCitation box="[1072,1132,631,653]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 4aa, bb, 5aa).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(bb)Pale yellow mark around median ocellus small, broken into four spots, posterior pair sometimes missing (
<figureCitation box="[1289,1349,660,682]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
: 4aa, bb, 5aa).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,780,719,741]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(cc) Clypeus dull, with distinct surface microsculpture. … 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[768,780,719,740]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">5</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</keyLead>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<keyLead pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[151,191,748,770]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,191,748,770]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">5(4)</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,220,1239]" box="[199,1105,777,799]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
(a) Head color pattern 
<figureCitation box="[432,491,777,799]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
