<keyLead box="[151,828,1217,1239]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
– (aa) Clypeus anteriorly largely pale yellow (
<figureCitation box="[628,688,1217,1239]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="40.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-424@40.[151,1435,1264,1906]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="FIGURE 4. Key to Onycholyda species 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876505" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876505/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
